title: "Delta Diamond Fish" (w/ Shangela)

description:
A Star Is HERE on Las Culturistas!

Matt sits down with the ONE AND ONLY Shangela Laquifa Wadley (Ru Paul's Drag Race, A Star is Born) to talk all things A Star Is Born. Halleloo! 

Topics include: working with Bradley Cooper and Lady Gaga, hanging with Gaga at Soho House in London, comebacks, breaking bones onstage, loving yourself, and so much more! 

Plus, Shangela reveals her plan to become the first drag queen to perform on all 7 continents. Antartica, get ready for Shangela's Happy Feet number!
